text: Akho, ki maim ko'i anokha nabi nahim ham ate maim nahim janada ki mere nala ki saluka kita javega. Ate tuhade nala ki saluka kita javega. Maim`tam sirafa usa da hi palana karada ham jihara mere vala vahi (prakasana) de rahim a'unda hai. Ate maim tam sirafa ika pratakha savadhana karana vala ham
